('q_observed_probe__leaf_yellowing__yellowing_primary_clue_gate',
 '黄叶原因较复杂，先选你最明显看到的一类线索。这样后面会按方向继续问，避免问很多无关问题。',
 'single_choice','leaf_yellowing','observed_probe__leaf_yellowing__yellowing_primary_clue_gate',1,'high','yellowing_primary_clue_gate','differential_probe','gate','route_gate',1,260,'audited','data_layer_template','runtime must not hardcode this yellowing gate copy',
 '黄叶原因较复杂，先选你最明显看到的一类线索。这样后面会按方向继续问，避免问很多无关问题。',
 '只选最明显的一类；如果看不准，可以先选日常养护或不确定。',
 '黄叶需要先分流养护、虫害、病斑或单纯黄叶，避免后续问题全部偏向单一路径。',
 'care_context','single_select_accordion','data_template','qge_yellowing_primary_clue_gate','manual','question_data_layer_templates_20260429','v20260429_data_layer_templates','audited','黄叶首层 gate 由数据层治理，默认进入养护方向。',1,NOW(),NOW(),NOW(),'question_data_layer_templates_20260429'),
('q_observed_probe__leaf_yellowing__yellowing_care_area_gate',
 '为了判断黄叶是否和日常养护有关，先选最近两周最可疑的一项。每个选项下面有参考说明，选最接近你实际情况的即可。',
 'single_choice','leaf_yellowing','observed_probe__leaf_yellowing__yellowing_care_area_gate',1,'high','yellowing_care_area_gate','context_probe','gate','route_gate',1,250,'audited','data_layer_template','runtime must not hardcode this yellowing care gate copy',
 '为了判断黄叶是否和日常养护有关，先选最近两周最可疑的一项。每个选项下面有参考说明，选最接近你实际情况的即可。',
 '这题不是让你直接判断病因，而是先决定继续查浇水、光照、施肥还是通风湿度。',
 '养护方向需要先细分到具体行为，再进入对应的频率或环境问题。',
 'watering_area','single_select_accordion','data_template','qge_yellowing_care_area_gate','manual','question_data_layer_templates_20260429','v20260429_data_layer_templates','audited','黄叶养护 gate 由数据层治理，默认从浇水方向开始。',1,NOW(),NOW(),NOW(),'question_data_layer_templates_20260429'),
('q_observed_probe__leaf_yellowing__watering_frequency_context',
 '最近 2 周，你的浇水间隔更接近哪一种？',
