 '最近 2 周，你的浇水间隔更接近哪一种？',
 '{{watering_help}}',
 '浇水频率用于判断黄叶是否可能和根区长期偏湿或偏干有关。',
 '','single_select_accordion','data_template','qge_yellowing_watering_frequency_context','manual','question_data_layer_templates_20260429','v20260429_data_layer_templates','audited','浇水周期题由数据层模板治理，选项文字由变量渲染。',1,NOW(),NOW(),NOW(),'question_data_layer_templates_20260429'),
('q_observed_probe__leaf_yellowing__light_change_context',
 '最近 1-2 周，这盆植物每天大概能晒到多久的直射太阳？',
 'single_choice','leaf_yellowing','observed_probe__leaf_yellowing__light_change_context',1,'medium','light_change_context','context_probe','context_metric','context_feature',1,230,'audited','data_layer_template','light question template is governed in data layer',
 '最近 1-2 周，这盆植物每天大概能晒到多久的直射太阳？',
 '这里问的是直射太阳时长，不是室内亮不亮；后续会结合植物本身的耐光情况判断是否偏强或偏弱。',
